                          <h2 style="color:#03acb4;font-weight:bold;">How It Started</h2>
                          <h2 style="font-weight:bold;">1985</h2>
                          <p>CEO Masami Sakaguchi established SEIHA English Academy. It is a private Eikawa English conversation school run by SEIHA Network Co, Ltd. It started primarily in western Japan aiming to teach children from 3 months old to 14 years old. Native English-speaking teachers co-teach in tandem with native Japanese teachers. SEIHA’s curriculum specializes in using Total Physical Response as its core teaching model. </p>
