                          <h2 style="font-weight:bold;">December 2015</h2>
                          <p>Seiha English Network Philippines Incorporated, also known as UPTALK Seiha, was founded in 2015. It offers online classes for students in Japan. Our teachers obtain high English credentials and are confidently fluent in teaching English lessons online.  SEIHA teachers work hand-in-hand and are supervised and supported proactively by our Filipino and Japanese managers. Seiha Method of teaching, developed by Seiha English Academy, is strictly applied in the Philippine branch. Uptalk Seiha is currently situated in FLB Corporate Center, Archbishop Reyes, Cebu City, Philippines</p>
