                          <h2 style="color:#31a400;font-weight:bold;margin-top:10px;">70,000</h2>
                          <p>SEIHA’s number of students had reached 70, 000 at the beginning of 2019.</p><br />
                          <p>Seiha has schools all over Japan from Hokkaido to Okinawa. It has 900 locations all around Japan and approximately 2,500 teachers, overall. The number of students strengthened its status of being the largest children’s English school in Japan.</p>
