                          <h2 style="color:#5500ff;font-weight:bold;margin-top:10px;">Seiha Global<br />Academy</h2>
                          <h2 style="font-weight:bold;">March 2019</h2>
                          <p style="margin-top:30px;">With the influx of foreign tourists wanting to learn English while enjoying the beautiful beaches of Cebu, Seiha English Academy saw an opportunity to expand a second branch and offer an offline teaching model. Seiha Global Academy Incorporated was officially opened. By the end of March, it offered its first classes, catering to Japanese adults and children for face-to-face lessons and excursions in Cebu.</p><br />
                          <p>True to its company values - Expansion and Advancement, SEIHA sets its gaze on extending its reach to other countries in the future.</p>
